  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the psychological, physical, social, professional and family impact of a&#xD;
      hospitalization in intensive care for a covid 19 by analysis of the verbatim during a&#xD;
      semi-structured interview.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
